info.title: Singapur client-api
info.description:
Client API to Singapore Project 
 The client api have the common methods in relation to the user register in the platfform, and offer access to all the functionalities so that the client can manage their profile and operate with the services offered by professionals 
 The operation are:
 -Login
 -Password change, this includes different cases, such as the voluntary change, restoring a forgotten password and reseting it.
 -Check token
 -Email validation
 -Client creation
  Url Confluence https://steps.everis.com/confluence/display/PROLEMER/Endpoint+Login+Client#EndpointLoginClient-Login
